{"article_id":"0AkhHy3AegweX7NZ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US infectious disease chief Dr Anthony Fauci is being targeted by the Trump administration","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"as tensions rise between the health expert and the president .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"The White House has been increasingly critical of Dr Fauci ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"and on Sunday , an official shared a list","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"detailing past apparent erroneous comments .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Dr Fauci 's changing advice on masks and remarks on Covid-19 's severity are among the points from the White House .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"The move","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to undercut him","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"comes as the US continues to see surges in Covid-19 .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"There are over 3.3 million cases","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"confirmed and more than 135,000 deaths nationwide ,","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"according to Johns Hopkins University .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Dr Fauci has contradicted President Donald Trump 's comments on the pandemic a number of times ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"pushing back on the president 's claims","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that the outbreak is improving","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and attributing hasty state reopenings to the recent surges .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"The White House memo","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"leaked over the weekend","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"had noted","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` several White House officials are concerned about the number of times","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Dr Fauci has been wrong on things '' .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Though the White House said","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Dr Fauci and Mr Trump have a `` good working relationship '' on Monday ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Trump adviser Peter Navarro told CBS News :","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"`` When you ask me","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"if I listen to Dr Fauci 's advice ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"my answer is only with caution . ''","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"During a law enforcement event at the White House on Monday , Mr Trump said :","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"`` I have a very good relationship with Dr Fauci .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"I 've had for a long time -","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"right from the beginning . `` I find him to be a very nice person .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"I do n't always agree with him . ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"The president added :","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"`` I get along with him very well .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"I like him personally . ''","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Mr Trump earlier on Monday retweeted comments from a game show host","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"accusing `` everyone '' ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"including the US Centers for Disease Control","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"( CDC ) ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"of lying about the coronavirus .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"White House press secretary Kayleigh McEnany later told reporters","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Mr Trump still had confidence in the CDC","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"and the tweet was meant to express his displeasure with `` some rogue individuals ''","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"who leaked planning documents .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"Echoing the contents of the anti-Fauci memo earlier ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Mr Navarro , an economic adviser to Mr Trump , said","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Dr Fauci `` has been wrong about everything","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"I have ever interacted with him on '' .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"`` When I warned in late January in a memo of a possibly deadly pandemic ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Fauci was telling the media not to worry , ''","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Mr Navarro said","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Dr Fauci fought against Mr Trump 's `` courageous decision ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"to halt flights from China ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"initially said","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"the virus was `` low-risk ''","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and `` flip-flopped on the use of masks '' .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"`` Now Fauci is saying","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"that a falling mortality rate does n't matter","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"when it is the single most important statistic","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"to help guide the pace of our economic reopening . ''","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Admiral Brett Giroir , assistant US health secretary and member of the virus task force , told NBC News on Sunday","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"while he respects Dr Fauci ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"he is not always right .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"`` Dr Fauci is not 100 % right","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"and he also does n't necessarily ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"he admits that ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"have the whole national interest in mind .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"He looks at it from a very narrow public health point of view . ''","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"As cases and deaths continue to rise in a number of states ,","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"Mr Trump has been accused by critics of politicising health issues ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"including wearing masks .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Mr Trump has also clashed with the World Health Organization","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"( WHO ) ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"accusing the body of mismanaging the pandemic","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"when it began","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"and failing to make `` greatly needed reforms '' .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"On 7 July , he formally began to pull the US out of the WHO","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"funding would be redirected .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Donald Trump has often railed against newspapers","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"that publish anonymous quotes from administration aides critical of the president .","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"Over the weekend , however , the White House was using its own unnamed `` officials '' in a remarkable attack on a member of its coronavirus task force , top infectious disease expert Anthony Fauci .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"The White House even provided a list of Fauci 's old statements about the virus similar to the kind of memo","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"a campaign might use","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"to direct negative attention on a political opponent .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"The administration ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"it appears ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"is trying to paint Fauci as wrong about the early threat of the virus and , consequently , untrustworthy","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"when he questions the administration 's analysis of the current situation and its planned actions .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"As if that was n't enough ,","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"on Monday morning the president retweeted a post by former game show host Chuck Woolery ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"accusing the Centers for Disease Control , among others , of lying about the virus in an effort","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"to undermine the Trump 's re-election prospects .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"An administration at war with its own scientific and medical experts in the middle of a pandemic","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"that is once again on the upswing","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"makes developing a cohesive strategy","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"- one","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"that the public trusts","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"and will follow -","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"challenging , to say the least .","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"More from Anthony :","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"Things","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"US has got wrong","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"- and got right","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"Dr Fauci has not weighed in on the White House memo ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"but he has remarked on his recent lack of television appearances .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"`` I have a reputation ,","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"as you probably have figured out ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"of speaking the truth at all times","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"and not sugar-coating things , ''","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"he told the Financial Times on 10 July .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"`` And that may be one of the reasons","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"why I have n't been on television very much lately . ''","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Dr Fauci also said","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"he has not seen Mr Trump in person since 2 June","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"and has not briefed him for the last two months .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"The infectious disease chief has instead been appearing on livestreams and podcasts .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"On 9 July , he told FiveThirtyEight :","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"`` As a country ,","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"when you compare us to other countries ,","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"you can say","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"we 're doing great .","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"I mean ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"we 're just not . ''","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"Dr Fauci participated in a livestream with Stanford University Medical School on Monday afternoon ,","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"but did not directly address the White House comments .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"A New York Times/Siena College poll at the end of June found","depth":5},{"id":130,"text":"67 % of US voters trusted Dr Fauci","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"regarding the pandemic ,","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"with just 26 % expressing trust in Mr Trump .","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"In February , Dr Fauci did not advise Americans to change their behaviour due to the pandemic ,","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"but he did note","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"the situation was evolving .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"During an interview with the Today morning programme on 29 February , Dr Fauci said :","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"`` Although the risk is low now ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"you do n't need to change anything","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"you 're doing ,","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"when you start to see community spread ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"this could change . ''","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"At the time , there were fewer than 100 cases in the US .","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"In early March , Dr Fauci and other health officials did advise against having the public wear masks .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"He did , at the time , note","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"that infected individuals should wear one","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"to prevent spreading the disease .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"Dr Fauci has defended his earlier comments on masks ,","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"citing new research","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"and saying","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"it was due to concerns over scarcity at the time for healthcare providers .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"He has since strongly recommended wearing face coverings in public .","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"A career official , Dr Fauci has advised six presidents","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"- Republican and Democratic -","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"on health issues ,","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"including the HIV/AIDs epidemic .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"He has been the director of the National Institutes of Health Allergy and Infectious Diseases division since 1984 .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":313,"left":237,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":217,"right":236,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":217,"left":191,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":158